|Daniel 7   
| style=&quot;background: #f7f6f6;&quot;|Winged Lion is Medo-Persia   
| style=&quot;background: #ffee7a;&quot;|Lopsided Bear is Macedonia   
| style=&quot;background: #e2e2e0;&quot;|Leopard is Ptolemys &amp; Seleucids   
| style=&quot;background:#cc9;&quot;|Iron-toothed beast is Romans   
| style=&quot;background: #cdfcfd;&quot;|Future antichristian empire   
