| style=&quot;background: #f7f6f6;&quot;|Ram is Medo-Persia   
| style=&quot;background: #ffee7a;&quot;|Goat is Macedonia  
| style=&quot;background: #e2e2e0;&quot;|Little Horn is Seleucids   
| style=&quot;background:#cc9;&quot;|The &quot;Son of Man&quot; cleanses the Sanctuary during the Roman occupation   
