==Compatibility==
The service is still compatible with '''ONdigital''' and [[ITV Digital]] boxes, though loading speeds are slower than newer Freeview boxes.  The BBC has not announced if support for the older boxes would be discontinued.  The [[Teletext Ltd.|''Teletext'']] service from the UK commercial broadcasters had stopped supporting the old boxes in 2005. As of 2010, the ONdigital boxes only load pages 100 and 199 and some interactive services that use channel 301, if any other page is loaded it exits the service.

Page numbers were introduced in 2004 to aid navigation, with 3-digit page numbers matching with those of the analogue Ceefax in 2006.  Pages exclusive to digital are given a four digit number.

